lyrics:
(Verse 2)
Headlights cut through the dust, stars peekin' through
City lights in the distance, what's there to lose?
Sing along to every verse, voices mergin'
Feelin' alive, young and wild, hearts forever surgin'

(Chorus)
Packed a bowl, fire it up, let the smoke fly
Local Natives on the speakers, hummin' real high
Wind in our hair, asphalt unwindin'
Just another summer night, freedom we're findin'
